{"tid":1946892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(強勢回歸) 何志平或於6月8日出獄　護照過期料需遣返","createTime":"2020-03-28T02:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T03:52:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"da0441ed18f09f94c959408354d9327f8b689416","tid":1946892,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200327/photo/bkn-20200327214827250-0327_00972_001_01p.jpg?20200327221457\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200327%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200327214827250-0327_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20200327221457&h=a5438f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民政事務局前局長何志平去年在美國被判行賄罪成，入獄3年；他其後上訴，但至今未有結果。據美國聯邦監獄局資訊，何志平將於本年6月8日獲釋，他前後服刑時間約為2年半。<br />\n<br />\n何志平被指以在美國為基地的非政府組織作掩飾，賄賂乍得及烏干達政府高層官員，替中國華信能源公司爭取石油生意等商機，於2017年11月在美國紐約被捕。他其後被裁定7項罪名成立，包括5項違反海外反腐敗法、一項串謀洗錢罪及一項洗錢罪，被判囚和罰款。<br />\n<br />\n據報，何志平的上訴申請已在本月中獲審理，但未有結果；即使上訴不成功，只要他行為良好，加上扣減還押在紐約大都會懲教中心的16個月，何志平料可於6月獲釋。不過，由於何志平的護照已過期，不能合法在美國逗留，預料即使上訴成功，他亦不能立即獲釋。美國政府之前已預告，會在他出獄後遣返他。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200327/bkn-20200327214827250-0327_00972_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b9069be5e5b8c13193d7718998015a8b61d25c8e","tid":1946892,"uid":331251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"253c1d9f01dba5030972558a0b8d1c5c8e7f09ae","tid":1946892,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"何醫生返黎可以幫手抗疫 ...."},{"pid":"dc700ae789279ad75bbf6d6fa7c9c3313e287e5b","tid":1946892,"uid":331949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"藩籬無命了"},{"pid":"fe813ff5bbace4fa35c596c4414789e36e5b0285","tid":1946892,"uid":14486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"直送北京了"},{"pid":"dc6a589f9f56d474b718617f7de723cd624e264c","tid":1946892,"uid":54824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:34:46.000Z","msg":"坐飛機點揀香港 <br />\n順便中埋武漢肺炎<br />\n直送 火葬場"},{"pid":"5292f9cd85589a3a3ff30ae8e773b506cd672469","tid":1946892,"uid":154763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:47:40.000Z","msg":"佢知太多嘢，隨時被消失"},{"pid":"fce2a7de5904758a3b6f00b4b3db2b42e6cb43f5","tid":1946892,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"直接確診 死亡 火化<br />\n一條龍專機服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8c8aa01728744e32e55d0b4f886edf3990a20c","tid":1946892,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9069be5e5b8c13193d7718998015a8b61d25c8e","tid":1946892,"uid":331251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:50:29.000Z","msg":"點會無deal"},{"pid":"0c7bfe41c246f9e6357404639e84e0a5dff23273","tid":1946892,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:51:02.000Z","msg":"希望佢中肺炎"},{"pid":"34bb051de5d1760930fb193379f36fa35dd4c4bf","tid":1946892,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"知咁多秘密<br />\n要空中解體了"}]}